    <section id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-title">Mission</div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <p>Raja Rani Coaching, our mission is simple yet profound: to empower individuals with the artistry and craftsmanship of tailoring, enabling them to pursue their dreams with confidence and skill. We believe in fostering creativity, innovation, and professionalism in every stitch.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-title">Vision</div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <p>Our vision is to create a community of proficient tailors who not only master the technical aspects of the craft but also embrace its artistic and entrepreneurial dimensions. We envision a world where the legacy of tailoring thrives, and every garment tells a story of skill, passion, and precision.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-title">Our Approach</div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <p>At Raja Rani Coaching, we take a holistic approach to tailoring education, blending traditional techniques with modern practices. Our experienced instructors provide hands-on training, personalized guidance, and industry insights to ensure that each learner develops a strong foundation and a unique style in tailoring.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-title">Meet Our Instructors</div>
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <p>Our team of instructors comprises seasoned professionals with years of experience in the field of tailoring and fashion design
                                . Passionate about sharing their knowledge and skills, they are committed to guiding and inspiring learners on their journey to mastery.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-title">Our Courses</div>
                            <div class="card-content">
                                <p>We offer a comprehensive range of courses designed to cater to all skill levels and interests. From basic sewing skills to advanced pattern making and garment construction, our curriculum is carefully crafted to equip learners with the knowledge and expertise needed to succeed in the competitive fashion industry.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-title">Our Community</div>
                            <div class="card-content">
                                <p>Join our vibrant community of aspiring tailors, where you can connect with fellow learners, share ideas, seek advice, and celebrate your progress. Whether you're a beginner or an experienced tailor, you'll find a supportive and inclusive environment to nurture your passion and hone your craft.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    
